OL,3,C'Parents can be aggressive': four in
OL,4,Cfive school leaders abused in last year
OL,6,FMore than four in five school leaders
OL,7,Fsay they have been abused in the past
OL,8,Fyear, a survey has revealed.
OL,10,F82% of leaders in Wales said they have
OL,11,Fbeen subjected to verbal, physical or
OL,12,Fonline abuse, according to a poll by
OL,13,Fthe National Association of
OL,14,FHeadteachers (NAHT).
