OL,3,C'Parents can be aggressive': four in
OL,4,Cfive school leaders abused in last year
OL,6,FAlthough verbal abuse was the most
OL,7,Fcommon experience of abuse reported by
OL,8,Fschool leaders in the past year, over
OL,9,Fone in ten also reported being
OL,10,Fsubjected to physical violence.
OL,12,FIt comes as the NAHT said they
OL,13,Freceived widespread reports of
OL,14,Ftrolling on social media, as well as
OL,15,Fin online parent groups.
OL,17,FA third of leaders said they
OL,18,Fexperienced abuse from parents
OL,19,Fmonthly, with 14% saying it is a
OL,20,Fweekly occurrence.
