OL,3,C'Parents can be aggressive': four in
OL,4,Cfive school leaders abused in last year
OL,6,FAlun Ebenezer, headteacher at Caldicot
OL,7,Fschool told ITV Wales that their
OL,8,F'strict, no-nonsense' approach to
OL,9,Fdiscipline received initial resistance
OL,10,Ffrom parents.
OL,12,FHe said: "I think that parents can be
OL,13,Faggressive, they can have a sense of
OL,14,Fentitlement. When I first came to
OL,15,FCaldicot, there was definitely a
OL,16,Freaction from parents against what we
OL,17,Fwere trying to do. I don't see that
OL,18,Fnow. I think initially, people
OL,19,Fquestioned our approach, what we're
OL,20,Ftrying to do. Now, I think almost
OL,21,Feveryone buys into that approach."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
