OL,3,C'Parents can be aggressive': four in
OL,4,Cfive school leaders abused in last year
OL,6,FHe added: "Initially, of course young
OL,7,Fpeople react against that, they don't
OL,8,Fwant that, or so they think. But once
OL,9,Fthey see it working, it actually makes
OL,10,Fthem happier, feel safer, it makes
OL,11,Ftheir lessons better.
OL,13,F"It's hard, if it wasn't hard, every
OL,14,Fschool would be doing it. But it has
OL,15,Fbeen a strict, no-nonsense, firm
OL,16,Fboundary, strict discipline
OL,17,F(approach)."
