OL,3,C'Parents can be aggressive': four in
OL,4,Cfive school leaders abused in last year
OL,6,FDespite the initial backlash from
OL,7,Fparents, Mr Ebenezer noted: "When I
OL,8,Ftalk about firm boundaries, strict
OL,9,Fdiscipline, no-nonsense... I get a pat
OL,10,Fon the back. Until it's their child.
OL,12,F"Everybody wants high standards until
OL,13,Fit's their child- because it's hard
OL,14,Fisn't it, it's hard bringing up
OL,15,Fteenagers I'm not pretending that it's
OL,16,Fnot. But when they know that we are
OL,17,Fsticking to our guns, and 'no' doesn't
OL,18,Feventually turn into 'yes' and parents
OL,19,Fcan see that working and the impact it
OL,20,Fhas, they eventually get on board."
