OL,6,FOne senior leader in Wales explained:
OL,7,F"Nasty emails are becoming more
OL,8,Ffrequent. I receive abusive emails
OL,9,Foften from parents without any thought
OL,10,For any balance."
OL,12,FAnother said: "Slanderous vexatious
OL,13,Fcomplaints which are targeted at
OL,14,Findividual members of staff."
