OL,3,C'Parents can be aggressive': four in
OL,4,Cfive school leaders abused in last year
OL,6,FLaura Doel, NAHT Cymru national
OL,7,Fsecretary, said: "These results lay
OL,8,Fbare a worrying trend emerging in
OL,9,FWelsh schools whereby verbal and in
OL,10,Fextreme cases physical abuse is
OL,11,Fbecoming part of the job. This is
OL,12,Fsimply unacceptable. It cannot be the
OL,13,Fcase that school leaders are subjected
OL,14,Fto this kind of treatment and more
OL,15,Fneeds to be done to protect them.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
