OL,3,C'Parents can be aggressive': four in
OL,4,Cfive school leaders abused in last year
OL,6,F"NAHT Cymru is calling on local
OL,7,Fauthorities to work with us to tighten
OL,8,Fup complaints procedures and stand up
OL,9,Fto this abusive behaviour, ensuring
OL,10,Fschools are safe and nurturing
OL,11,Fenvironments for all staff and pupils."
OL,13,FIn a statement, the Welsh Government
OL,14,Fsaid: "Any form of violence or abuse
OL,15,Fagainst staff in our schools is
OL,16,Fcompletely unacceptable. Children are
OL,17,Fbest supported where parents and
OL,18,Fschools can work together, and where
OL,19,Fthere is mutual respect and support.
